data.description: Lovely two bedroom villa with a private courtyard and fully fenced back yard located in Wellington. The screened-in patio offers a relaxed setting for morning coffee, or dining al fresco. The floor plan has been modified to an airy, expansive living space with a wet bar. The high vaulted ceiling adds a light and bright feel to the cozy home. Hidden Landing is a wonderful neighborhood with a low monthly HOA payment, and lakeside saltwater community pool. Conveniently located in close proximity to The International Polo Center, Winter Equestrian Festival, and The Global Dressage Festival. There are wonderful restaurants and shops close-by, A-rated schools, and beautiful parks. Palm Beach International Airport is about 25 minutes away. Palm Beach is a straight shot via Southern Blvd.
